Dialogue: 5,0:00:02.19,0:00:04.11,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,A Grande Era dos Piratas...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:04.11,0:00:09.07,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,provou ser uma tempestade mais turbulenta\Ndo que o World Government esperava.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:10.91,0:00:18.12,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,As figuras no olho dessa\Ntempestade implacável são...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:20.00,0:00:21.83,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,Monkey D. Luffy...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:23.13,0:00:25.13,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,e os Piratas do Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:27.51,0:00:31.39,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,Para confrontar a furiosa Grande Era dos Piratas,
Dialogue: 5,0:00:31.39,0:00:35.85,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,cinquenta líderes mundiais se reuniram\Npara esta conferência quadrienal:
Dialogue: 5,0:00:36.72,0:00:39.94,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,a Reverie, que terá início em breve.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:44.69,0:00:48.32,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,Agora é um tempo de grandes mudanças.
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=28=58}=========================OPENING NARRATION============================
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{=28=47}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 5,0:00:57.00,0:00:58.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tô com fome!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:02.33,0:01:03.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que é isso?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:05.55,0:01:07.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Onde você achou isso?!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:07.21,0:01:09.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã? Eu achei no meu bolso.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:09.80,0:01:11.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Legal! É de verdade?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:11.80,0:01:13.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que é?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:13.05,0:01:14.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você não lembra?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:15.14,0:01:18.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\t(2479,3021,1,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}É o que a Germa usava pra se transformar!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:18.27,0:01:19.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, é verdade!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:19.98,0:01:22.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu vou me transformar com isso!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:22.40,0:01:24.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espera! Eu vou primeiro!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:25.61,0:01:27.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Sanji!\N– Sanji!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:27.32,0:01:29.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu vou me livrar disso.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:29.69,0:01:30.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– O quê?!\N– O quê?!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:30.99,0:01:32.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não ouse jogar fora!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:32.82,0:01:35.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se jogar, eu procuro no fundo do mar!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:35.70,0:01:38.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quero ver uma âncora como você tentar!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:38.49,0:01:42.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tava no meu bolso. Se você não quer,\Nme dá isso!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:42.54,0:01:44.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não, me dá! Por favor!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:44.96,0:01:45.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,De jeito nenhum!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:47.21,0:01:51.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas eu me pergunto como\Nisso foi parar no bolso do Luffy.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:52.09,0:01:53.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Deve ter sido o Niji.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:53.59,0:01:55.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele fez pra me provocar.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:58.14,0:02:03.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu não quero que minha força venha\Nda tecnologia porcaria deles!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:03.19,0:02:04.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\pos(392,1053)}Pense bem, Sanji!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:04.90,0:02:07.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1572,1053)}Ciência é um nobre\Npoder humano!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:07.77,0:02:09.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Por que você se importa tanto?!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:09.82,0:02:13.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,981)}– Se a gente usasse o raid suit...\N– Se a gente usasse o raid suit...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:18.70,0:02:21.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– talvez a gente pudesse disparar raios!\N– talvez a gente pudesse disparar raios!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:21.00,0:02:22.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês são crianças?!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:22.75,0:02:24.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O Franky já faz isso muito bem!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:24.62,0:02:26.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Já temos aberrações suficientes na tripulação.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:26.96,0:02:28.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não! É meu!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:28.00,0:02:31.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê? Você tava zombando da ciência?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:31.26,0:02:33.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nami-swan!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:33.13,0:02:36.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,De jeito nenhum que eu insultaria sua ciência!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:36.26,0:02:42.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Meu Bastão Climático Mágico é a fusão de\Nciência celeste e engenharia do Usopp!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:43.14,0:02:43.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Olha!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:48.40,0:02:50.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu simplesmente {\i1}amo{\i0} ficar dentro do bastão dela!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:50.94,0:02:52.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Zeus?!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:52.28,0:02:54.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você realmente veio junto?!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:54.03,0:02:56.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não acredito que comida é mais importante\Nque sua lealdade à Big Mom!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:56.86,0:02:59.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}♪ Eu arrumei um servo poderoso! ♪
Dialogue: 5,0:02:59.28,0:03:00.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,N-Nami...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:01.91,0:03:03.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Zeus, lembre-se disso...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:04.58,0:03:08.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu sirvo a Nami desde muito\Nantes de você aparecer!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:08.50,0:03:13.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas {\i1}eu{\i0} moro no bastão que ela\Nleva consigo o tempo todo!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:13.51,0:03:15.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:15.05,0:03:17.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sanji, você tá discutindo com vapor d'água.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:17.89,0:03:20.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Certo! Vamos!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:21.56,0:03:23.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Por que não tá funcionando?!\N– Por que não tá funcionando?!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:23.81,0:03:24.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Para de choramingar!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:24.56,0:03:27.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Acho que só funciona em você!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:27.44,0:03:29.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mostra logo pra gente!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:29.27,0:03:30.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cala a boca!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:30.19,0:03:32.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu não faço parte da Germa!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:32.19,0:03:38.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Escutem! "Germa 66" e "Vinsmoke" são\Ndois nomes que eu nunca mais quero ouvir!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:38.66,0:03:40.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Obrigado!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:41.41,0:03:44.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por favor, se transforme!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:42.74,0:03:44.50,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,M-Me soltem, seus idiotas!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:44.50,0:03:45.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, galera!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:45.75,0:03:47.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O jornal chegou!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:47.83,0:03:50.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tem alguma coisa sobre a gente?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:50.00,0:03:51.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos ver...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:52.46,0:03:53.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um close do Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:54.59,0:03:55.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E o Jinbe?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:55.92,0:03:58.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Diz o que aconteceu depois que a gente saiu?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:59.05,0:04:02.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã... Jinbe, Jinbe...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:02.05,0:04:04.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sem notícias do que aconteceu depois que saímos...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:04.27,0:04:09.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Só que "Luffy, Sanji, Jinbe e Bege fizeram uma\Ntentativa de assassinato contra a Big Mom."
Dialogue: 5,0:04:09.52,0:04:11.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E que "Luffy foi o mentor intelectual"!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:11.77,0:04:12.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,"Mentor intelectual"?!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:14.40,0:04:15.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, cartazes de recompensa!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:17.65,0:04:19.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Minha recompensa aumentou!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:19.03,0:04:21.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}São 330 milhões de berries!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:21.37,0:04:22.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sério?!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:22.95,0:04:25.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espera, quanto tava a do Cabeça de Musgo?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:25.20,0:04:27.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Acho que a do Zoro tava em...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:27.21,0:04:29.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,320 milhões de berries!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:29.54,0:04:31.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Consegui!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:31.71,0:04:33.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tô acima daquele maldito Cabeça de Musgo!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:33.80,0:04:35.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\pos(288,926)}É só um número.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:35.92,0:04:40.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles mudaram "apenas vivo"\Nde volta pra "vivo ou morto"!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:43.35,0:04:46.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã? O que houve?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:46.14,0:04:47.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Meu nome...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:51.44,0:04:53.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá escrito "Vinsmoke Sanji"!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:53.94,0:04:55.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Faz sentido...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:55.53,0:04:59.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Minha recompensa só aumentou\Npor causa da fama da Germa!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:59.61,0:05:02.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,S-Sanji! Você tá bem?!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:02.32,0:05:06.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?! Tem uma aura ainda mais sombria\Nvindo dali!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:08.25,0:05:09.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,L-Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:09.66,0:05:11.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que houve?!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:15.46,0:05:17.63,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,Enquanto isso...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:19.05,0:05:23.59,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,O mundo está alvoroçado com a Reverie...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:23.59,0:05:28.85,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,a cúpula mundial realizada a cada quatro anos\Nna Terra Sagrada de Mary Geoise.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:30.14,0:05:34.65,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,Esta é a Ilha dos Homens-Peixe,\N10.000 metros abaixo do nível do mar.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:34.65,0:05:37.61,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,O Reino de Ryugu.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:37.61,0:05:39.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele conseguiu-jamon!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:39.82,0:05:43.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O Jinbe finalmente entrou pra tripulação do Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:45.07,0:05:49.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}É inacreditável pensar que os dois\Nlutaram juntos contra a Big Mom.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:49.54,0:05:52.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Será que eles escaparam no mesmo navio?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:52.42,0:05:55.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Jinbe e Chapéu de Palha-fá-sol-lá-si-dó! ♪
Dialogue: 5,0:05:55.71,0:06:00.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Claro que sim. O artigo diz\Nque a Big Mom ficou furiosa.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:01.42,0:06:07.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Precisamos declarar oficialmente que nosso país\Nestá sob a proteção dos Chapéu de Palha-jamon!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:07.22,0:06:09.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Querido Pai! Queridos Irmãos!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:12.48,0:06:14.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Shirahoshi.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:15.19,0:06:17.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Permitam que eu vá à Reverie com vocês!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:17.90,0:06:22.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Eu preciso ir, ou o Senhor Luffy\Nvai me chamar de Medroshoshi de novo!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:26.78,0:06:29.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu estava esperando você tomar essa decisão!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:29.33,0:06:31.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Certo, vamos!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:32.12,0:06:33.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:35.88,0:06:42.92,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,Porém, ofuscando a Reverie que se aproxima\Ne chocando o público está a notícia de que
Dialogue: 5,0:06:42.92,0:06:48.14,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,o pirata novato Chapéu de Palha Luffy\Nenfrentou a Imperatriz Big Mom,
Dialogue: 5,0:06:48.14,0:06:50.77,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,alguém cuja posição não havia\Nvacilado em décadas.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:51.64,0:06:53.60,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,O artigo afirma o seguinte:
Dialogue: 5,0:06:54.31,0:06:57.98,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,"Uma fonte confiável confirmou\Nque o Chapéu de Palha Luffy
Dialogue: 5,0:06:57.98,0:07:01.57,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,assumiu o comando de\Nsete poderosas tripulações piratas.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:01.57,0:07:06.82,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,Essa manobra o torna\Ncomandante de 5.000 subordinados.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:07.78,0:07:11.33,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,Nota-se que tanto Ace quanto o número dois\Ndo Revolutionary Army, Sabo,
Dialogue: 5,0:07:11.33,0:07:13.96,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{\t(1853,0,1,\c&H000000&)}são considerados seus irmãos de juramento.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:14.96,0:07:20.80,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele convenceu o exército maligno Germa 66,\Nos Piratas do Sol e os Piratas Fire Tank
Dialogue: 5,0:07:20.80,0:07:25.42,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{\t(4103,0,1,\c&H000000&)}a segui-lo sem hesitação,\Ntudo graças à sua liderança e carisma.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:26.01,0:07:30.97,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,Sua estratégia astuciosa resultou na\Ndestruição do castelo da imperatriz.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:32.14,0:07:36.06,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele derrubou dois de seus comandantes valendo\N800 milhões e 1 bilhão respectivamente.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:37.02,0:07:41.07,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,Portanto, é natural considerar\No Chapéu de Palha Luffy o vitorioso!"
Dialogue: 5,0:07:41.86,0:07:45.03,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,E assim, o artigo conclui\Ncom uma proclamação:
Dialogue: 5,0:07:45.99,0:07:49.87,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,526)}"O Quinto Imperador emergiu!"
Dialogue: 5,0:07:53.24,0:07:56.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que papo é esse de "Quinto Imperador"?!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:56.50,0:08:02.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}É só escória pirata causando problemas,\Nsejam Quatro Imperadores ou Cinco Imperadores.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:05.63,0:08:08.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tenho um relatório pra você,\NAlmirante de Frota Sakazuki!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:08.76,0:08:13.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A caminho da Reverie,\Npiratas emboscaram o navio de Lulusia!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:14.02,0:08:18.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O rei não foi ferido,\Nmas a Princesa Comane foi sequestrada.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:18.31,0:08:20.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Onde estava a escolta da Marinha?!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:25.78,0:08:26.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Xeque.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:30.03,0:08:32.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vovô! Vovô!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:33.33,0:08:34.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que foi, Rebecca?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:34.79,0:08:35.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Olha!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:36.08,0:08:38.33,Main-207+,,0,0,2,,E aí? Você leu a notícia sobre o Lucy?!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:38.33,0:08:40.17,Main-207+,,0,0,2,,Sim. Li sim.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:40.17,0:08:41.33,Main-207+,,0,0,2,,Ah, tá...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:41.33,0:08:43.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O Luffyland é incrível!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:43.71,0:08:46.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esse é nosso chefe!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:46.30,0:08:50.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}O artigo mencionou a gente também.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:51.39,0:08:56.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Todos, quando chegarmos à Terra Sagrada,\Nvocês não podem falar sobre isso.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:56.27,0:08:58.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê? Por que não?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:58.35,0:09:01.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A gente pode ser grato a ele,
Dialogue: 5,0:09:01.73,0:09:05.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,mas o World Government\Ne os Marinheiros o veem diferente.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:06.15,0:09:08.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Verdade! Ele é um pirata!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:08.53,0:09:13.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Exatamente. E agora ele tá ganhando\Numa reputação extraordinariamente perigosa.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:13.70,0:09:15.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele é realmente algo.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:15.20,0:09:17.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, é! Preciso mostrar pra Viola!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:18.16,0:09:19.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos mostrar!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:23.42,0:09:28.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sem dúvida. Aqueles navios pertencem\Naos Reinos de Dressrosa e Prodence!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:28.30,0:09:30.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sem escolta da Marinha também!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:30.67,0:09:34.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oh! A-Aquela é a Princesa Viola!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:34.01,0:09:36.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ela é tão linda quanto dizem.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:36.43,0:09:38.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aquela outra garota também é da realeza?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:38.85,0:09:42.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos poder pedir quanto quisermos\Nse sequestrarmos elas também.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:43.85,0:09:46.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Certo, Princesa Comane?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:47.11,0:09:49.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Só liga pro Papa logo!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:49.65,0:09:52.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele vai pagar o quanto vocês quiserem!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:54.07,0:09:56.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por isso que eu gosto de famílias reais!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:56.33,0:09:58.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Só aguenta mais um pouquinho.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:58.12,0:10:00.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A gente é bem ganancioso.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:00.12,0:10:04.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,De qualquer forma, eles não vão nos ver chegando...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:04.67,0:10:07.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,já que estamos escondidos debaixo d'água!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:07.63,0:10:08.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Afundem eles!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:08.80,0:10:09.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entendido!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:11.59,0:10:15.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É impossível se defender de um torpedo!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:36.57,0:10:37.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê...?!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:38.28,0:10:39.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uma emboscada?!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:40.16,0:10:41.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Preparem os canhões!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:41.45,0:10:42.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Sim, senhor!\N– Sim, senhor!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:44.08,0:10:45.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não! Não precisa!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:50.30,0:10:51.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que bom que cheguei a tempo!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:51.92,0:10:53.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês estão seguros agora!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:53.59,0:10:55.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,V-Você é um Marinheiro?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:56.97,0:10:59.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sou o Capitão Koby do Quartel-General da Marinha!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:00.56,0:11:02.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Erramos o alvo?!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:02.10,0:11:03.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Impossível!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:06.90,0:11:10.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos afundar!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:10.40,0:11:12.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês não estão feridos?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:14.90,0:11:17.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seu grupo veio de\NDressrosa e Prodence, certo?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:17.99,0:11:19.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês devem estar cansados, viajando tão longe.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:19.99,0:11:22.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que acabou de acontecer?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:22.37,0:11:24.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Como você chegou aqui?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:27.54,0:11:30.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tive que ir na frente do meu navio.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:31.67,0:11:36.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Agora pouco, piratas estavam\Nmirando em vocês de debaixo d'água.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:36.13,0:11:37.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,"Debaixo d'água"...?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:37.89,0:11:39.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quer dizer com um torpedo?!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:39.60,0:11:41.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que bom que erraram!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:41.64,0:11:42.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Também acho.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:44.48,0:11:46.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Helmeppo! Relatório!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:46.85,0:11:48.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Capturamos os piratas!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:53.48,0:11:54.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Olha!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:55.07,0:11:57.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}A Princesa Comane de Lulusia também está bem!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:57.82,0:11:59.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Seus malditos...!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:59.24,0:12:01.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Assem esses cretinos num espeto!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:01.37,0:12:02.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Eles precisam pagar!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:02.99,0:12:05.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Claro, eles vão pagar caro, Princesa!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:05.70,0:12:10.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Aliás, qual é o lance do seu Haki\Nde observação, Koby?!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:10.71,0:12:14.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu nem senti o torpedo.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:16.55,0:12:17.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um submarino...?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:17.88,0:12:20.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tem que ter cuidado com\Nos piratas hoje em dia...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:20.55,0:12:22.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Essa foi por pouco.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:22.26,0:12:23.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Olá!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:25.06,0:12:27.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então, você é o famoso Capitão Koby!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:27.56,0:12:28.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:28.69,0:12:30.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Do Incidente de Rocky Port?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:30.98,0:12:37.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Trafalgar Law, um da Pior Geração,\Nfoi o mentor intelectual daquele incidente.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:37.19,0:12:40.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você é o herói que protegeu os cidadãos.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:42.32,0:12:45.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,N-Não, eu não sou herói nenhum!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:45.20,0:12:48.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você não é só corajoso,\Né um ótimo rapaz!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:48.41,0:12:51.29,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Uau... Esse cara é forte...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:51.63,0:12:55.50,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele acabou de nos salvar de um torpedo,\Ne não quer crédito nenhum?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:55.50,0:12:56.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Obrigado!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:56.92,0:12:58.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não foi nada...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:58.55,0:13:00.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah! Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:00.55,0:13:03.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quer dizer, Chapéu de Palha Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:03.05,0:13:05.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O artigo de capa chamou minha atenção.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:05.68,0:13:07.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você quer ler, Koby?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:07.14,0:13:10.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não, não. Bom, quer dizer, sabe...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:14.69,0:13:16.82,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,"O Quinto Imperador."
Dialogue: 5,0:13:18.11,0:13:21.57,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,O Luffy continua incrível como sempre!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:22.66,0:13:25.24,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele não para de avançar!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:26.24,0:13:27.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Koby?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:32.58,0:13:36.55,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Toda vez que te vejo no jornal,\Neu penso naquele dia...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:40.80,0:13:42.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Capitão Koby!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:42.09,0:13:44.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que você tá fazendo? Volta logo!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:44.30,0:13:45.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Certo!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:49.89,0:13:51.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Muito obrigado!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:52.69,0:13:53.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por nada.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:54.44,0:14:01.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Estamos perto de New Marineford,\Npermitam que os escoltemos o resto do caminho!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:02.32,0:14:04.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Agradeço.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:05.41,0:14:06.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, ei!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:08.08,0:14:09.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que foi?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:09.20,0:14:11.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você gosta do Lucy, Koby?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:11.33,0:14:13.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você gosta do Luffyland, né?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:13.21,0:14:15.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,N-Não! E-Ele é meu inimigo!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:15.83,0:14:17.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não nos engana!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:17.96,0:14:19.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A gente não conta.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:19.51,0:14:21.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fica e conversa.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:21.26,0:14:25.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,M-Me soltem, por favor! E-Eu sou da Marinha!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:25.26,0:14:28.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas você parecia tão feliz\Nquando leu o jornal.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:28.06,0:14:29.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I-Isso é porque...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:29.64,0:14:32.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos. Vamos conversar!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:30.89,0:14:32.43,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,P-Por favor, parem!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:32.85,0:14:35.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, o Luffyland tá nesse artigo aqui também!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:35.56,0:14:36.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá?!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:36.61,0:14:39.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então você gosta dele!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:46.87,0:14:47.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:48.83,0:14:51.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ter minha recompensa aumentada\Npor causa da reputação da Germa...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:52.33,0:14:55.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,é muito deprimente.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:58.29,0:15:00.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, você tá bem?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:00.71,0:15:02.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seus ferimentos doem?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:03.42,0:15:05.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,N-Não!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:05.80,0:15:07.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Minha...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:09.18,0:15:12.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Minha recompensa caiu!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:12.98,0:15:14.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Olha!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:14.10,0:15:16.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,São 150 milhões de berries!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:16.06,0:15:17.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– O quê?!\N– O quê?!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:18.81,0:15:22.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sério?! Eu achei que tinha acabado\Nde subir pra 500 milhões!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:22.86,0:15:26.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cento e cinquenta milhões é menor\Nque sua recompensa de dois anos atrás!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:26.99,0:15:29.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Como isso é possível?!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:29.58,0:15:31.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você fez alguma coisa errada?!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:31.87,0:15:33.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso não faria ela aumentar?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:33.37,0:15:35.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, é verdade.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:37.88,0:15:39.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não é tão ruim assim.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:39.04,0:15:40.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Menos gente vai vir atrás da gente.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:40.92,0:15:42.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:42.50,0:15:43.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy é nosso capitão!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:43.92,0:15:46.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso pode prejudicar nossa reputação!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:46.18,0:15:49.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que droga! Por quê?!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:51.76,0:15:53.89,Main-207+,,0,0,8,,Preparem os canhões!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:53.89,0:15:56.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fogo à vontade!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:00.11,0:16:02.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:02.61,0:16:05.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Peguem o dinheiro e os objetos de valor!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:05.82,0:16:07.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cadê os Marinheiros?!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:07.70,0:16:10.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles já não tinham vindo ajudar?!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:11.66,0:16:13.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles destruíram nosso navio!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:15.95,0:16:17.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:24.25,0:16:26.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que se danem os Marinheiros!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:26.92,0:16:29.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O rei deles foi pra Reverie.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:29.55,0:16:33.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Todos os melhores soldados foram com ele!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:33.14,0:16:38.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um país indefeso é praticamente\Num convite pra piratas saquearem!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:39.56,0:16:41.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Agora escutem bem!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:43.19,0:16:46.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Eu sou afiliado ao Barba Negra,\Num dos Quatro Imperadores!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:46.78,0:16:50.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Me apelidaram de Barba Rosa!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:50.78,0:16:52.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Lembrem-se do meu nome!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:52.95,0:16:55.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Temam o Barba Negra!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:57.04,0:16:58.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Muito bem, rapaziada!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:58.83,0:17:02.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Em nome do Barba Negra, peguem tudo!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:09.34,0:17:11.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá, passem o dinheiro!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:11.80,0:17:13.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,P-Por favor, parem!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:14.81,0:17:16.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não adianta esconder!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:16.89,0:17:19.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos queimar a cidade inteira!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:22.23,0:17:23.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:23.73,0:17:24.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos sair daqui!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:31.70,0:17:33.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, pega aquela garota!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:36.16,0:17:38.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pare aí!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:39.79,0:17:42.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que é isso nos seus braços?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:42.58,0:17:47.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me deixa ver o que você tá\Nsegurando com tanta força!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:48.51,0:17:49.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso é...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:49.34,0:17:51.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã? Só leite?!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:52.38,0:17:54.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E eu achando que era dinheiro...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:54.05,0:17:56.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Dane-se! Vou levar mesmo assim.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:56.64,0:17:58.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês não podem! Isso é pras crianças da vila!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:58.31,0:18:00.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês não podem! Isso é pras crianças da vila!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:00.43,0:18:01.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cala a boca!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:07.44,0:18:10.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você tá sendo bem teimosa com isso!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:13.32,0:18:15.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por favor, devolva!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:15.07,0:18:16.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esse leite...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:16.83,0:18:19.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não podemos ficar sem ele!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:19.16,0:18:20.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:20.33,0:18:23.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então tragam dinheiro no lugar!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:23.04,0:18:24.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:24.08,0:18:25.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu não tenho nenhum.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:25.96,0:18:28.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês não têm um fundo de tributo celestial?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:29.67,0:18:34.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O-O tributo celestial é pro\Nrei e pros Celestial Dragons.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:34.76,0:18:39.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É tudo que conseguimos fazer, economizando\Ne poupando cada dia!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:39.72,0:18:43.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seremos executados se não\Npagarmos o tributo celestial!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:43.19,0:18:44.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:44.31,0:18:47.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esse rei de vocês parece horrível!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:47.06,0:18:48.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, tá bom!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:49.98,0:18:52.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, rapaziada, procurem!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:52.40,0:18:55.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles estão escondendo o tributo celestial!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:56.87,0:18:58.28,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}O dinheiro tá guardado!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:58.28,0:18:59.49,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Peguem tudo que eles têm!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:58.62,0:18:59.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas por quê?!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:00.45,0:19:02.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos! Diga onde tá o tributo!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:02.91,0:19:04.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nos deixem em paz...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:04.67,0:19:06.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Essa cidade é pobre.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:06.25,0:19:08.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,P-Por favor, menos o fundo!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:08.38,0:19:09.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Solta!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:11.46,0:19:13.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Alguém...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:13.26,0:19:16.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você não teria se machucado\Nse tivesse desistido!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:16.72,0:19:19.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Matem quem resistir!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:21.06,0:19:22.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu estou implorando!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:22.52,0:19:25.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por favor, nos deixem em paz!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:25.56,0:19:26.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cala a boca!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:30.32,0:19:32.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vai, Morley!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:33.94,0:19:35.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem diabos é você?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:38.53,0:19:40.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que tá tremendo?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:50.04,0:19:52.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tem algo no subsolo?!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:00.60,0:20:01.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que diabos?!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:01.85,0:20:03.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um tridente gigante?!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:11.15,0:20:12.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso é um gigante?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:12.52,0:20:15.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um, dois! Um, dois!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:15.94,0:20:18.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um, dois! Um...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:18.36,0:20:20.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,dois!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:25.37,0:20:28.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Um gigante acabou de subir\Ndireto do chão!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:28.87,0:20:31.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E ele tá vestido muito estranho!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:32.17,0:20:35.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã, por que ele tá usando uma minissaia?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:37.01,0:20:40.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que nojo! Pra onde você\Nacha que tá olhando?!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:43.76,0:20:46.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que tá me encarando?!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:46.77,0:20:49.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você tá a fim de mim ou algo assim?!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:49.85,0:20:52.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você realmente tá me acusando disso?!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:52.11,0:20:54.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Qual é a desse velho sujo?!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:54.90,0:20:57.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Só atira nele! Mata ele!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:57.65,0:20:58.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:00.07,0:21:02.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Para de babar em cima de mim, bobinhos!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:05.91,0:21:09.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,G-Gigantes vivem no subsolo?!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:09.92,0:21:11.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Primeiro que eu vejo...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:11.42,0:21:13.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem é ele, afinal?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:13.21,0:21:16.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não sejam tão maldosos!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:16.09,0:21:18.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:18.34,0:21:21.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Como isso é possível?! Ele tá empurrando\No chão como se fosse argila!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:21.47,0:21:24.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não vacilem! É só o poder dele!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:25.01,0:21:26.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Incrível!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:26.64,0:21:29.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E aí...? O que vocês vão fazer agora?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:30.06,0:21:31.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seus servis...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:32.27,0:21:34.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,pedaços de lixo.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:34.06,0:21:36.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê? Lixo?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:36.19,0:21:38.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que a gente faz?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:38.57,0:21:39.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Com licença!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:39.53,0:21:42.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem são...? Quem são vocês?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:53.12,0:21:54.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oh, meu!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:55.04,0:21:56.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Venham, venham!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:56.34,0:21:58.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espera um pouquinho, Morley!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:59.34,0:22:01.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que você quer?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:02.43,0:22:05.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, por favor! Eu queria testar\Nminha última invenção,
Dialogue: 5,0:22:05.85,0:22:08.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,mas você saiu correndo na frente!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:08.31,0:22:10.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem são essas pessoas?!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:16.77,0:22:18.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uma revoada de corvos?!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:19.23,0:22:20.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Capitão!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:20.24,0:22:20.86,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:20.86,0:22:23.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,T-Tem alguém no telhado!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:23.66,0:22:25.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:25.70,0:22:27.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Os corvos estão se juntando...!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:36.71,0:22:40.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Como vocês ousam machucar aqueles\Nque não oferecem resistência.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:41.97,0:22:45.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Capitão Barba Rosa... aqueles quatro...!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:45.89,0:22:48.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,148)}Eles normalmente estão espalhados pelo mundo!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:49.35,0:22:50.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,144)}Eles são os comandantes...
Dialogue: 5,0:22:51.39,0:22:53.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,do Revolutionary Army!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:54.48,0:22:56.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O q... O q...
Dialogue: 5,0:22:56.27,0:22:59.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:00.86,0:23:03.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ei, eles ainda tão me encarando.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:05.36,0:23:08.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Se controlem, lixos!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:09.16,0:23:12.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Me permitam testar minha nova arma!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:13.83,0:23:17.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Vocês não vão mais fazer o que querem.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:18.71,0:23:20.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Os comandantes do...
Dialogue: 5,0:23:20.75,0:23:22.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Revolutionary Army?
Dialogue: 5,0:23:28.68,0:23:30.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Rinhá!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:30.89,0:23:33.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Aquele Chapéu-de-Palinha é algo!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:33.56,0:23:36.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ele com certeza tem o seu sangue.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:37.31,0:23:38.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}E...
Dialogue: 5,0:23:38.56,0:23:42.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,quem diria que o Sanji-nho\Nera um príncipe da Germa 66?!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:42.78,0:23:46.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele nunca me falou uma palavra sobre isso!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:46.20,0:23:47.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que trapaceiro!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:47.91,0:23:52.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Essa confusão levou à expulsão da Germa\Ndo World Government.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:52.62,0:23:57.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não esperava menos do\NChapéu-de-Palinha e do Sanji-nho.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:57.54,0:24:01.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Eles são a força motriz\Nda Grande Era dos Piratas!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:01.92,0:24:05.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Os Chapéu de Palha... Que emoção!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:05.97,0:24:09.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Enfim, os comandantes estão atrasados.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:09.72,0:24:12.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Eles já deveriam ter chegado.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:12.56,0:24:14.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É verdade...
Dialogue: 5,0:24:14.31,0:24:15.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A propósito, Sabo...
Dialogue: 5,0:24:15.93,0:24:18.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,o que você tá fazendo aí?
Dialogue: 5,0:24:20.61,0:24:25.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele tá sorrindo desde que leu a notícia\Nsobre o Luffy, e o rosto travou, né?
Dialogue: 5,0:24:25.65,0:24:27.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que bobão!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:30.37,0:24:31.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aqui é o Lindbergh!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:31.62,0:24:34.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que houve? Todos estão esperando.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:34.08,0:24:35.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}É o Sabo?
Dialogue: 5,0:24:35.20,0:24:37.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Estamos quase lá.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:37.04,0:24:38.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mas encontramos uns problemas!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:38.87,0:24:40.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se importam se a gente se atrasar um pouco?
Dialogue: 5,0:24:41.13,0:24:43.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entendido. Só fiquem inteiros.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:44.96,0:24:47.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, estou tão empolgado!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:47.13,0:24:51.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Todos os oficiais do\NRevolutionary Army vão estar aqui!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:51.22,0:24:53.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vou ver o Comandante Morley!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:53.97,0:24:56.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A Mestra Betty é minha favorita!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:56.98,0:25:01.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sabo, o relógio tá correndo. Precisamos começar.
Dialogue: 5,0:25:01.23,0:25:04.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seria melhor finalizar\No plano antes deles chegarem.
Dialogue: 5,0:25:04.73,0:25:07.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É com você, Chefe de Estado-Maior.
Dialogue: 5,0:25:07.69,0:25:08.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É.
Dialogue: 5,0:25:09.20,0:25:13.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Na próxima Reverie, finalmente vamos...
Dialogue: 5,0:25:15.12,0:25:17.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}...declarar guerra...
Dialogue: 5,0:25:18.37,0:25:20.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}contra os Celestial Dragons.
Dialogue: 5,0:25:22.29,0:25:23.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então eles são...
Dialogue: 5,0:25:24.34,0:25:25.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,os comandantes do...
Dialogue: 5,0:25:26.46,0:25:27.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Revolutionary Army!
Dialogue: 5,0:25:31.01,0:25:33.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que quatro dos oficiais deles estão aqui?!
Dialogue: 5,0:25:33.89,0:25:36.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nossa, vocês garotos são brutos!
Dialogue: 5,0:25:36.51,0:25:39.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Talvez porque eles gostam\Nde você, seu grandalhão!
Dialogue: 5,0:25:39.39,0:25:41.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,De jeito nenhum. Que nojento!
Dialogue: 5,0:25:41.19,0:25:45.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Falei com o Sabo,\Nentão vamos começar, Betty?!
Dialogue: 5,0:25:45.77,0:25:47.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não tem como me parar.
Dialogue: 5,0:25:48.57,0:25:50.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Parece que eles não vão responder minha pergunta.
Dialogue: 5,0:25:50.95,0:25:53.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E o que aquele cara tá\Nresmungando lá?!
Dialogue: 5,0:25:53.74,0:25:56.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu considero suas ações imperdoáveis!
Dialogue: 5,0:25:56.33,0:25:58.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que ele tá tão furioso?!
Dialogue: 5,0:25:58.83,0:26:02.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Qual vai ser, seus pedaços de lixo?!
Dialogue: 5,0:26:02.21,0:26:03.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês vão morrer?
Dialogue: 5,0:26:03.75,0:26:04.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ou vão lutar?!
Dialogue: 5,0:26:06.42,0:26:09.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Escolham seu destino!
Dialogue: 5,0:26:11.80,0:26:14.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que deixar ser herói pra outra pessoa?!
Dialogue: 5,0:26:18.06,0:26:20.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Vocês podem ser heróis!
Dialogue: 5,0:26:41.04,0:26:45.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Os moradores pegaram paus!\NVamos! Não me façam rir!
Dialogue: 5,0:26:45.79,0:26:48.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês vão lutar contra a gente?!
Dialogue: 5,0:26:50.30,0:26:54.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não sei por quê, mas estou inspirado\Ne sinto uma onda de energia!
Dialogue: 5,0:26:54.43,0:26:56.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos expulsar esses piratas daqui!
Dialogue: 5,0:26:57.18,0:26:59.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Devemos lutar pra proteger nosso país!
Dialogue: 5,0:27:02.35,0:27:03.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo!
Dialogue: 5,0:27:03.73,0:27:06.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esse é o poder da Fruta Rally-Rally da Betty!
Dialogue: 5,0:27:06.86,0:27:11.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ao agitar sua bandeira, ela pode despertar\No poder latente em qualquer pessoa!
Dialogue: 5,0:27:11.61,0:27:14.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Betty é a porta-bandeira da liberdade!
Dialogue: 5,0:27:14.82,0:27:17.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Agora, avancem!
Dialogue: 5,0:27:23.41,0:27:25.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Acho que eles não sabem que dói levar um tiro!
Dialogue: 5,0:27:25.67,0:27:27.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Preciso botar vocês no lugar!
Dialogue: 5,0:27:29.88,0:27:32.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Lind! Karasu! Deem apoio a eles!
Dialogue: 5,0:27:32.63,0:27:34.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entendido!
Dialogue: 5,0:27:34.88,0:27:35.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tomem essa!
Dialogue: 5,0:27:35.68,0:27:38.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Cool Shooter!
Dialogue: 5,0:27:38.55,0:27:39.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que frio!
Dialogue: 5,0:27:39.80,0:27:41.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Minha arma congelou!
Dialogue: 5,0:27:41.60,0:27:44.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seus desgraçados!\NCaiam fora daqui, piratas!
Dialogue: 5,0:27:46.81,0:27:50.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não vacilem! Cortem eles!
Dialogue: 5,0:27:50.15,0:27:51.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Peguem as armas deles!
Dialogue: 5,0:27:57.45,0:27:59.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Os corvos pegaram nossas espadas!
Dialogue: 5,0:27:59.57,0:28:00.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Devolvam!
Dialogue: 5,0:28:00.78,0:28:02.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não parem!
Dialogue: 5,0:28:02.58,0:28:04.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não se rendam ao destino!
Dialogue: 5,0:28:04.25,0:28:06.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Lutem!
Dialogue: 5,0:28:07.08,0:28:09.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se mandem!
Dialogue: 5,0:28:13.96,0:28:17.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que deu neles de repente?!
Dialogue: 5,0:28:17.09,0:28:19.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me devolve...
Dialogue: 5,0:28:19.51,0:28:20.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,de volta...
Dialogue: 5,0:28:23.39,0:28:26.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,meu leite!
Dialogue: 5,0:28:45.29,0:28:46.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos vazar!
Dialogue: 5,0:28:46.45,0:28:48.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso não acabou!
Dialogue: 5,0:28:49.71,0:28:53.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Barba Rosa... tem uma recompensa de 52 milhões.
Dialogue: 5,0:28:54.88,0:28:58.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O Imperador Barba Negra vai vir atrás de vocês...
Dialogue: 5,0:28:58.72,0:29:02.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Infelizmente pra vocês,\Naquele homem pouco se importa com seus subordinados.
Dialogue: 5,0:29:03.10,0:29:06.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, garoto! Cala essa boca!
Dialogue: 5,0:29:08.77,0:29:12.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, seus covardes,\Nfrouxos e patéticos palhaços!
Dialogue: 5,0:29:15.02,0:29:18.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se vocês entregarem ele ao World Government...
Dialogue: 5,0:29:18.03,0:29:19.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,vocês podem reivindicar a recompensa.
Dialogue: 5,0:29:20.66,0:29:24.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,São 52 milhões de berries.
Dialogue: 5,0:29:24.03,0:29:25.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E...
Dialogue: 5,0:29:25.12,0:29:27.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,é tudo de vocês!
Dialogue: 5,0:29:29.66,0:29:32.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Além disso, quero que fiquem com isso.
Dialogue: 5,0:29:33.33,0:29:36.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usem isso pra contatar o Revolutionary Army.
Dialogue: 5,0:29:40.09,0:29:42.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês foram ótimos...
Dialogue: 5,0:29:42.30,0:29:43.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 5,0:29:44.64,0:29:46.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nos chamem a qualquer hora.
Dialogue: 5,0:29:46.76,0:29:48.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A gente nunca vai virar as costas...
Dialogue: 5,0:29:49.39,0:29:52.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,pros fracos que querem se levantar.
Dialogue: 5,0:30:03.57,0:30:06.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,M-Mestra Belo Betty!
Dialogue: 5,0:30:12.37,0:30:15.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Obrigado por tudo, Revolutionary Army!
Dialogue: 5,0:30:24.59,0:30:28.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, pra que a gente tá se reunindo dessa vez?
Dialogue: 5,0:30:29.02,0:30:31.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos comprar briga\Ncom os Celestial Dragons.
Dialogue: 5,0:30:31.52,0:30:35.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, essa é a melhor notícia! Mal posso esperar!
Dialogue: 5,0:30:35.19,0:30:36.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, e Karasu!
Dialogue: 5,0:30:37.52,0:30:39.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Liga seu amplificador de voz.
Dialogue: 5,0:30:42.95,0:30:44.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esqueci.
Dialogue: 5,0:30:46.62,0:30:49.49,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,Faltam dois dias para o início da Reverie.
Dialogue: 5,0:30:49.49,0:30:54.12,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,Todas as peças ao redor do mundo\Ncomeçam a se unir.
Dialogue: 5,0:30:55.54,0:30:57.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tá, entendido.
Dialogue: 5,0:30:58.25,0:31:00.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eram os outros, Sabo.
Dialogue: 5,0:31:01.30,0:31:03.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eles vão chegar em breve.
Dialogue: 5,0:31:03.13,0:31:04.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Certo!
Dialogue: 5,0:31:05.80,0:31:07.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos seguir em frente.
Dialogue: 5,0:31:10.64,0:31:13.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que diabos?!
Dialogue: 5,0:31:13.14,0:31:19.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Por que aquele moleque que ferrou\Ncom meu valioso negócio de SMILE...
Dialogue: 5,0:31:19.52,0:31:22.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}tava no território daquela velha?!
Dialogue: 5,0:31:30.24,0:31:33.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, então ele é o vitorioso?!
Dialogue: 5,0:31:33.66,0:31:34.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?!
Dialogue: 5,0:31:34.79,0:31:37.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quando exatamente eu perdi?!
Dialogue: 5,0:31:38.25,0:31:41.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Foi ele, Mama! Ele publicou esse artigo!
Dialogue: 5,0:31:41.25,0:31:44.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah, você vai pagar por isso, Morgans–
Dialogue: 5,0:31:44.63,0:31:45.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não!
Dialogue: 5,0:31:48.59,0:31:52.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quem realmente vai pagar...
Dialogue: 5,0:31:52.56,0:31:55.27,Main-207+,,0,0,2,,é o Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 5,0:31:57.35,0:31:59.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Um Imperador?
Dialogue: 5,0:31:59.11,0:32:01.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}É um pouco prematuro te chamar assim!
Dialogue: 5,0:32:12.66,0:32:15.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Parece que vou te ver em breve...
Dialogue: 5,0:32:17.71,0:32:18.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:32:28.05,0:32:31.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Então, sua recompensa caiu. O que a gente pode fazer?
Dialogue: 5,0:32:31.35,0:32:33.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Anima, Luffy.
Dialogue: 5,0:32:33.60,0:32:35.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Me deixa ajudar de algum jeito.
Dialogue: 5,0:32:35.18,0:32:36.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos fazer o que pudermos!
Dialogue: 5,0:32:36.56,0:32:39.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quer que eu cozinhe algo pra você?
Dialogue: 5,0:32:40.61,0:32:41.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É...
Dialogue: 5,0:32:45.82,0:32:46.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 5,0:32:47.53,0:32:49.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espera. Só. Um. Minuto.
Dialogue: 5,0:32:54.70,0:32:55.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Olha.
Dialogue: 5,0:32:56.25,0:33:00.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,100 mil, 1 milhão, 10 milhões...
Dialogue: 5,0:33:00.50,0:33:02.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,100 milh–
Dialogue: 5,0:33:04.96,0:33:07.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sua recompensa...
Dialogue: 5,0:33:10.18,0:33:13.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,é 1,5 bilhão de berries!
Dialogue: 5,0:33:13.97,0:33:19.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– O quê?!\N– O quê?!
Dialogue: 5,0:33:20.14,0:33:25.27,Narrator-207+,,0,0,0,,O mundo olha para a Reverie\Nenquanto a tripulação segue para Wano.
